----------------------------------------------------------------------------

To dynamically load g++ extension modules, you must recompile Python,
relink it using g++ (change LINKCC in the Python Modules Makefile), and
link your extension module using g++ (e.g., `g++ -shared -o mymodule.so
mymodule.o').


